Express 5 + TypeScript API with Zod validation.

## What you need to modify

Your project has 12 files. You only need to care about 3:

| File | What it does | When to edit |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `src/routes/index.ts` | All your API endpoints | **Every time** |
| `src/index.ts` | App setup + middleware wiring | Only when adding middleware |
| `tests/app.test.ts` | Tests for your endpoints | **Every time** |
| Others (eslint config, Docker, CI, AGENTS.md) | Project infrastructure | Almost never |

## Quick Start

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

The server starts at **http://localhost:3000/health**.

## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Start dev server with hot reload (`tsx watch`) |
| `npm run build` | Compile TypeScript to `dist/` |
| `npm start` | Run compiled production code |
| `npm test` | Run tests once (Vitest) |
| `npm run test:watch` | Run tests in watch mode |

